### About

This is a compilation of the various animal images such as bear, cat, dog, elephant, lion, goat, horse, lion, tiger and wolf


### Content
 This dataset has been compiled and arranged in the imagenet style:
-- mammals
    -- bear
        -- 00000.jpg
             ....
    -- cat
         -- 00000.jpg
              .....
     

### Acknowledgements

Compilation of this dataset is through the DuckDuckGo image download functionality, part of the fastback chapter 2. I would like to thank everyone associated with fast.ai, including but not limited to its contributor/developers, reading groups and community
